BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-18T23:37:00&endDate=2026-03-19T00:20:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Monday 16\, Tuesday 17\, Wednesday 18\, Thursday 19 and Friday 20 March\, the 2338 last train from Dalston Junction to West Croydon will be diverted to Crystal Palace\, arriving 0016. Customers for Penge West\, Anerley\, Norwood Junction and West Croydon should use the 2331 from Dalston Junction
DTEND:20260319T002000Z
