BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-25T22:15:00&endDate=2026-03-26T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWINDRUSH LINE: Monday 23\, Tuesday 24\, Wednesday 25 and Thursday 26 March\, after 2215 each evening\, no service between Sydenham and West Croydon. West Croydon trains will divert to and depart from Crystal Palace instead. Use local buses or Trams via any reasonable route or Southern trains between Sydenham and Norwood Junction. Tickets will also be accepted on Southern trains between Crystal Palace and Norwood Junction\, and between Norwood Junction and East Croydon. Last through trains: Highbury & Islington to West Croydon 2202\; West Croydon to Highbury & Islington 2246
